snippet.title: WATCH LIVE: Abortion rights on the line at Supreme Court in historic arguments | FOX 5 DC
snippet.description:
Abortion rights are on the line at the Supreme Court in historic arguments over the landmark ruling nearly 50 years ago that declared a nationwide right to end a pregnancy. DETAILS: https://bit.ly/3loD26a
